summary: This is an automated out-of-office email reply from an FBI Victim Specialist, indicating they will be unavailable until August 2, 2019, and directing urgent inquiries to another specialist. The email references case number 31E-MM-108062.
keyFacts: The document is an automated out-of-office reply from an FBI Victim Specialist dated July 26, 2019.
The specialist references case number 31E-MM-108062, indicating it is related to a victim report.
The specialist will be out of the office until August 2, 2019, and directs urgent matters to another Victim Specialist.
